DIGIMON EVERYWHERE
DIGIVOLVED TO MEGA!

9
00:00:17,724 --> 00:00:20,226
KNOWING THE DIGITAL WORLD
WAS IN GOOD HANDS,

10
00:00:20,226 --> 00:00:21,895
THE TAMERS PREPARED
TO GO HOME.

11
00:00:21,928 --> 00:00:24,898
BUT JUST AS THEY GOT WORD
THAT THE ARK WAS ON ITS WAY,

12
00:00:24,965 --> 00:00:26,633
RIKA AND RENAMON WENT OFF
TO FIND IMPMON.

13
00:00:26,666 --> 00:00:29,736
THEY BETTER HURRY UP, OR THEY'RE
GOING TO MISS THE BOAT.

14
00:00:31,571 --> 00:00:34,441
DI-DI-DI

